        <param>
          <type>UINTPTR</type>
          <declname>BaseAddress</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>This function returns a reference to an <ref refid="struct_x_dp_rx_ss___config" kindref="compound">XDpRxSs_Config</ref> structure based on the core id, <emphasis>DeviceId</emphasis>. </para>        </briefdescription>
